### -------------------------
### GET all users (empty list)
### -------------------------
GET http://localhost:5025/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### -------------------------
### POST valid user
### -------------------------
POST http://localhost:5025/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "Alice",
  "age": 30
}


### -------------------------
### POST invalid user (empty name)
### Expect: 400 Bad Request
### -------------------------
POST http://localhost:5025/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "",
  "age": 25
}


### -------------------------
### POST invalid user (age <= 0)
### Expect: 400 Bad Request
### -------------------------
POST http://localhost:5025/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "Bob",
  "age": 0
}


### -------------------------
### GET user by ID (existing)
### -------------------------
GET http://localhost:5025/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### -------------------------
### GET user by ID (non-existent)
### Expect: 404 Not Found
### -------------------------
GET http://localhost:5025/users/999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### -------------------------
### PUT update user (valid)
### -------------------------
PUT http://localhost:5025/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "Alice Updated",
  "age": 31
}


### -------------------------
### PUT update user (invalid name)
### Expect: 400 Bad Request
### -------------------------
PUT http://localhost:5025/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "",
  "age": 31
}


### -------------------------
### PUT update user (non-existent)
### Expect: 404 Not Found
### -------------------------
PUT http://localhost:5025/users/999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

{
  "userName": "Ghost",
  "age": 50
}


### -------------------------
### DELETE user (existing)
### -------------------------
DELETE http://localhost:5025/users/1
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### -------------------------
### DELETE user (non-existent)
### Expect: 404 Not Found
### -------------------------
DELETE http://localhost:5025/users/999
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### -------------------------
### GET users with pagination
### -------------------------
GET http://localhost:5025/users?skip=0&take=2
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken


### ============================
### MIDDLEWARE TESTS
### ============================

### 1) Missing token → Expect 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:5025/users
Accept: application/json


### 2) Invalid token → Expect 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:5025/users
Authorization: Bearer wrongtoken
Accept: application/json


### 3) Valid token → Expect 200 OK (or whatever your endpoint returns)
GET http://localhost:5025/users
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Accept: application/json


### 4) Trigger exception → Expect 500 Internal Server Error (error-handling middleware)
GET http://localhost:5025/users/throw
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Accept: application/json

